    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！　お待たせしました！\nステージは……琴乃ちゃんはどうなってますか！？",
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今は二曲目だ。あと四十秒で曲が終わるから\nそのタイミングでステージに上がってくれるか",
      "startTime": 11.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました！\n琴乃ちゃん……今行くよ。待っててね",
      "startTime": 16.1000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、本当によく頑張ってるよ\n見えるだろう？　この舞台袖からでも、あの表情が",
      "startTime": 24.033333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……凄い……",
      "startTime": 28.4666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "よし、曲が終わったぞ\nみんな、一緒に盛り上げてきてくれ！",
      "startTime": 35.0666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　行ってきます！",
      "startTime": 37.9000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日、MV撮影の現場にて",
      "startTime": 40.7333343506,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1666.6660308999965,
          "startTime": 42.4000003815
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "渚、お疲れ様。昨日のフェスから立て続けで\nハードだと思うが、頑張ってくれ",
      "startTime": 47.4333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　頑張っちゃいますよ～！",
      "startTime": 50.0333357492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "凄いやる気だな。何かいいことでもあったのか？",
      "startTime": 52.9999996184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……\nこの間まで目標についてず～っと悩んでましたけど……",
      "startTime": 59.5333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のフェスで、一人でステージに立つ琴乃ちゃんを\n見て……一気に考えがまとまりました",
      "startTime": 67.8333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが言ってくれたように\nきっかけ一つでこんなに変わるもんなんですね",
      "startTime": 74.1333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だからそんなにすっきりした顔をしてるのか\nでも、琴乃がきっかけってどういうことだ？",
      "startTime": 81.3666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "私達四人が駆け付けた時……一人であれだけ堂々と\n歌っていた琴乃ちゃんが、満面の笑みを浮かべたんです",
      "startTime": 90.0666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "あの後琴乃ちゃんに聞いたら、私達を見つけた瞬間に\n肩の力が抜けて、凄く安心したらしくて",
      "startTime": 99.4666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "それで私、思ったんです。「ああ、私には琴乃ちゃんが\n必要で……琴乃ちゃんも私のことが必要なんだ」って",
      "startTime": 110.8333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ステージでのほんの少しのやりとりだけで\n答えが見えることもあるんだな",
      "startTime": 119.0330620302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんとの関係は\n変わった部分も、もちろんあるけど……",
      "startTime": 123.0999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんを支えたい、っていう根っこの部分は\nやっぱり変わってませんでした",
      "startTime": 130.4999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだけじゃなくて……今は、私自身も輝いて\n胸を張って琴乃ちゃんと並び立ちたい",
      "startTime": 141.8000039418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "そして、お互いを支え合って……「お互いを一番近くで\n照らし合える関係」になりたいんです",
      "startTime": 152.2000039418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いい答えだと思う。それが、今の渚の目標なんだな",
      "startTime": 155.0666548409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "はい。それが、月ストを支えることにもなるのかなって",
      "startTime": 160.0333215075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "これなら歌番組のトークもばっちりだな\n期待してるよ",
      "startTime": 169.466676712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、ステージで琴乃ちゃんが私に手を伸ばして……",
      "startTime": 170.9999942777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_03-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "私が琴乃ちゃんの手をとった瞬間に物凄く大きな\n歓声が上がったのは……ちょっと恥ずかしかったですね",
      "startTime": 180.7590842549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
